t WordPress themes for bands and musicians? When it comes to the theme for a band or musician&#8217;s website, there are certain features and options that you need like a playlist, song player, video integration, event management, etc. In this article, we&#8217;ll share some of the best WordPress themes for [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes-for-bands/\">28 Best WordPress Themes for Bands and Musicians (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38364:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress themes for bands and musicians?</p>\n<p>When it comes to the theme for a band or musician&#8217;s website, there are certain features and options that you need like a playlist, song player, video integration, event management, etc.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share some of the best WordPress themes for bands and musicians that you can use.</p>\n<h3>Choosing a WordPress Theme for Bands and Musicians Website</h3>\n<p>WordPress themes for bands and musicians are unique in design. These themes will have a vibrant style and attractive layout. However, you need to make sure that the theme you&#8217;re selecting should offer the required features.</p>\n<p>A few key features that you&#8217;ll need from a band or musician theme are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatibility with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-event-plugins/\" title=\"9 Best WordPress Events Plugins Compared\">WordPress event management plugins</a></li>\n<li>Song player and wishlist creation</li>\n<li>Seamless integration with video player</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let&#8217;s take a look at some of the best WordPress themes for bands and musicians to create a music website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" title=\"Ultra\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">1. Ultra</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" title=\"Ultra\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ultra-music.jpg\" alt=\"Ultra\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233983\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ultra-music.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ultra-music-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ultra-music-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" title=\"Ultra\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Ultra</a> is a powerful WordPress theme for bands, musicians, DJs, and any music-related businesses. It has a colorful and bright background and the right set of features that are perfect for a music website. It comes with a fullscreen layout and no sidebars.</p>\n<p>This theme also has custom colors, parallax scrolling, and support for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\" title=\"7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders\">drag and drop page builder</a>. It&#8217;s easy to set up and looks great on all devices.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" title=\"Divi\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">2. Divi</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" title=\"Divi\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/divi-music.jpg\" alt=\"Divi\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233984\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/divi-music.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/divi-music-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/divi-music-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Divi is the most popular WordPress theme and page builder. It has tons of layouts and themes that you can use to create any website. With <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" title=\"Divi Builder\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Divi Builder</a>, you can easily drag and drop elements on your site. It comes with hundreds of content elements and modules.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s beginner friendly and supports WooCommerce to sell music online. Without a doubt, the Divi theme takes customization and flexibility to the next level.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">3. OceanWP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oceanwp-music.jpg\" alt=\"OceanWP\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233985\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oceanwp-music.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oceanwp-music-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/oceanwp-music-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oceanwp/\" title=\"OceanWP\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">OceanWP</a> is a multipurpose WordPress theme with dozens of demos for all kinds of websites. It features a perfect layout for band or music sites. This theme seamlessly integrates with popular drag and drop page builders like <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" title=\"Beaver Builder\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Beaver Builder</a>, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/elementor-pro/\" title=\"Elementor\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Elementor</a>, etc to create your layout.</p>\n<p>It comes with custom colors, backgrounds, navigation menus, sidebars, and widgets. You can use the WordPress live customizer to make changes in the theme.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra Theme\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">4. Astra Theme</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra Theme\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/astra-music.jpg\" alt=\"Astra\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-233986\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/astra-music.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/astra-music-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/astra-music-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/astra-wordpress-theme/\" title=\"Astra Theme\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Astra Theme</a> is a beautiful WordPress theme for musicians, bands, songs, and DJs. It has impressive features to create a playlist of your favorite bands and play songs online. The Astra theme is compatible with page builders, so you can build a site the way you want with drag and drop.</p>\n<p>The theme offers custom widgets, color schemes, full-width layout, and more. It&#8217;s highly customizable, lightning fast, and flexible to entertain your users.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/audiotheme-wayfarer/\" title=\"Wayfarer\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">5. Wayfarer</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/audiotheme-w