com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27760:\"<p>Are you wondering what the best Canadian web hosting is? If you want to create a website in Canada, it’s important that you choose a web hosting service that will give your website the speed, performance, and security it needs, but without breaking the bank. There are a ton of web hosting services on the market though, so it can be difficult to figure out which one is the best choice for you. </p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll share with you our top choices for the best Canadian web hosting services. We’ll go over U.S. based web hosting services that are great for Canadian websites as well as Canadian based web hosting providers. </p>\n<p>Let’s begin. </p>\n<h3>Canadian Web Hosting Review: Our Process</h3>\n<p>Before we share with your our choices for the best Canadian web hosting, let’s go over our IsitWP web hosting review process. </p>\n<p>Since we want to provide you with the most accurate review as possible, we’ve tested out many of these web hosting providers ourselves. We did this not only to provide a more detailed review, but also to help you choose the best Canadian hosting easier. It’s not practical for you to sign up for dozens of web hosting services and try them out, so we did the following steps for you: </p>\n<ol>\n<li>Signed up with the best Canadian web hosting providers on the market. </li>\n<li>Created a test WordPress website with a WordPress theme, dummy content, and images to mirror a live site environment. </li>\n<li>Conducted a few different speed tests to see how the site would perform.\n<li>Recorded the test data to share with you.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Now that you know how we got some of these web hosts stats and data, let’s jump into our #1 pick for the best Canadian hosting. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >1. Bluehost</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bluehost-canada.jpg\" alt=\"bluehost-canada-web-hosting\" width=\"370\" height=\"206\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-235095\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bluehost-canada.jpg 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bluehost-canada-300x167.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 689 ms</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.99%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 9/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"http://isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with Bluehost &raquo;</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Bluehost</a> is officially recommended by WordPress.org and it’s the most popular web hosting provider on the market, powering over 2 million websites worldwide.</p>\n<p>If you’re new to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-start-a-blog-step-by-step/\">starting a blog</a> or website, Bluehost is the best choice for you because of their affordability, scalability, and their helpful onboarding experience. </p>\n<p>Bluehost plans come with a free domain name for the 1st year, free SSL certificate, 1-click WordPress installation, unmetered bandwidth, and 24/7support. You can also try Bluehost out risk-free with their 30-day money back guarantee. </p>\n<p><strong> Servers in Canada</strong>: No, Utah, USA. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Regular pricing starts at CA$10.46/month. </p>\n<p><strong>Special Offer</strong>: IsItWP users only pay CA$3.60/month (Over 60% off + free domain name, SSL). </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/bluehost-review/\">Read our Bluehost review &raquo;</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >2. SiteGround</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/siteground-canada.jpg\" alt=\"siteground-canada-web-hosting\" width=\"370\" height=\"195\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-235099\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/siteground-canada.jpg 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/siteground-canada-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 649 ms</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.98%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 10/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">SiteGround.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with SiteGround &raquo;</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >SiteGround</a> is another one of the best Canadian web hosting providers, currently hosting about 2 million domains. It’s also one of the officially recommended hosting providers by WordPress.org. </p>\n<p>With SiteGround you can easily build a website, even without previous experience. They even giv