d pre-built sections.  </p>\n<p>All of their plans come with 1-click installs for apps such as WordPress, unmetered bandwidth, a free SSL certificate, and more. </p>\n<p>They offer a 45-day money back guarantee as well as always available technical support by phone, email, and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-live-chat-software-compared/\">live chat</a>.  </p>\n<p><strong>Servers in Canada</strong>: No, Houston and Utah, USA. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Regular price starts at $6.95/month. </p>\n<p><strong>Special Offer</strong>: Our users pay only $2.78/month. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/hostgator-review/\">Read our HostGator review >></a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpengine/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >4. WP Engine</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpengine/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpengine-canada-1.jpg\" alt=\"wpengine-hosting-services-canada\" width=\"740\" height=\"349\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-235102\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpengine-canada-1.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wpengine-canada-1-300x141.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpengine/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >WP Engine</a> is a managed WordPress hosting provider and it’s the platform of choice for over 2 million users, including big names like Yelp, National Geographic, Asana, and more. </p>\n<p>When you sign up with WP Engine, they give you access to 36 premium themes that include built-in SEO and security. Plus, they provide great 24/7/365 customer support to help you with anything you need. </p>\n<p>Although be warned, WP Engine is the most expensive web hosting provider on this list. </p>\n<p><strong>Servers in Canada</strong>: Yes, Montreal, Canada. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Regular pricing starts at $35/month. </p>\n<p><strong>Special Offer</strong>: Our users pay $28/month. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpengine/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Get started with WP Engine today >></a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >5. GreenGeeks</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/green-geeks-canada.jpg\" alt=\"best-canadian-web-hosting-greengeeks\" width=\"370\" height=\"186\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-235103\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/green-geeks-canada.jpg 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/green-geeks-canada-300x151.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 697 ms</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.92%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 9/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">GreenGeeks.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with GreenGeeks &raquo;</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >GreenGeeks</a> is one of the most well-known eco-friendly web hosting providers. So, if environmentally friendly web hosting is important to you, know that GreenGeeks puts back 3x the power they consume into the grid in the form of green energy. </p>\n<p>They provide some of the fastest, more secure, and scalable speed with data centers located in Toronto, Montreal, Chicago, Phoenix, and Amsterdam. You can also count on them to deliver awesome 24/7/365 customer support. </p>\n<p>Hosting plans with GreenGeeks offer unlimited web space, unlimited data transfer, free domain for the 1st year, 1-click WordPress installations, and much more. </p>\n<p><strong>Servers in Canada</strong>: Yes, Montreal, Canada. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Regular pricing starts at $9.95/month. </p>\n<p><strong>Special Offer</strong>: Our users pay only $2.95/month. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/greengeeks-review/\">Read our GreenGeeks review >></a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ipage/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >6. iPage</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ipage/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ipage-canada.jpg\" alt=\"ipage-web-hosting-canada\" width=\"370\" height=\"213\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-235104\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ipage-canada.jpg 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ipage-canada-300x173.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 2.60 s</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.98%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 8/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ipage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">iPage.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ipage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with iPage &raquo;</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/ipage/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >iPage</a> is another eco-friendly web hosting provider and they’re also one of the most affordable. iPage hosting gives you free domain registration, a drag and drop site builder, 1000s of free templates, a free SSL certificate, free email address, and more.</p>\n<p>All of the