la, Drupal, Magento, and more. </p>\n<p>A2 Hosting also offers an anytime money back guarantee. This means that if you’re not happy with their service within 30 days, you get a full refund. After the first 30 days, you’ll be eligible for a prorated refund for any unused services. </p>\n<p><strong>Servers in Canada</strong>: No, Michigan and Arizona, USA. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Regular pricing starts at CA$10.43/month. </p>\n<p><strong>Special Offer</strong>: Special offer pricing starts at only CA$3.68/month. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/a2-hosting-review/\">Read our A2 Hosting review >></a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hostpapa/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >8. HostPapa</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hostpapa/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/hostpapa-canada.jpg\" alt=\"hostpapa-best-canadian-hosting\" width=\"740\" height=\"380\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-235106\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/hostpapa-canada.jpg 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/hostpapa-canada-300x154.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hostpapa/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >HostPapa</a> is Canada’s #1 web host with over 500,000 websites hosted. Their web hosting provides you with a free domain name, reliable storage, unmetered bandwidth, over 400 apps including WordPress with 1-click installation, and more. </p>\n<p>HostPapa also offers their own website builder with a drag and drop interface, hundreds of professional templates, and you can even create an online store with their Enterprise plan. </p>\n<p>They also offer award-winning 24/7 email support backed by HostPapa’s in-house experts as well as telephone and live chat support in multiple lan