 small businesses. With Instagram, you can share details about your business in a visually stunning manner and connect to your audience that can possibly be your next client. So why not use this platform to expand your reach [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-instagram-plugins-wordpress/\">12 Best Instagram Plugins for WordPress in 2019</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22594:\"<p>Looking for the best Instagram Plugins for WordPress?</p>\n<p>Instagram is an excellent marketing platform for bloggers and small businesses. With Instagram, you can share details about your business in a visually stunning manner and connect to your audience that can possibly be your next client.</p>\n<p>So why not use this platform to expand your reach and possibly generate more sales? The best way to do that is by linking your Instagram profile to your business website. That way you can reach out to a wider audience and increase the possibility of converting more leads.</p>\n<p>If you are wondering how to connect your Instagram profile to your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-small-business-website-simple-steps/\" title=\"How to Create a Small Business Website in 5 Simple Steps\">business website</a>, we have got you covered. WordPress offers tons of plugins that let you do that effortlessly.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll show you some of the best Instagram plugins for WordPress that will let you display your Instagram feed right on your WordPress website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">1. Envira Gallery</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/envira-gallery-wordpress-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"Envira Gallery\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224643\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/envira-gallery-wordpress-plugin.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/envira-gallery-wordpress-plugin-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/envira-gallery-wordpress-plugin-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Envira Gallery </a>is one of the most popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\" title=\"8 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared\">WordPress gallery plugins</a> that helps you create visually striking photo and video galleries on your website. The plugin comes with a robust drag and drop builder that makes it possible to create a gallery within a few seconds. To make your gallery look more attractive, you can use the pre-built templates that the plugin offers.</p>\n<p>The plugin has been loaded with amazing built-in features. You can also extend its functionality with the help of addons. By activating these addons, you can integrate your website with any social platforms, including Pinterest and Instagram. Additionally, you can keep your albums organized, enable slideshows and full-screen lightbox mode, and do a lot more.</p>\n<p>With its WooCommerce addon, you can activate the eCommerce function too. Besides that, you can also protect your digital work by adding an extra layer of security which can either be a password, or a watermark.</p>\n<p>The plugin is fully responsive and is compatible with most of the popular plugins that you may be using on your website. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smashballoon-instagram-feed/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">2. Instagram Feed By Smash Balloon</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smashballoon-instagram-feed/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-Smash-Balloon.png\" alt=\"Instagram Feed- Smash Balloon, Instagram plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"396\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234782\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-Smash-Balloon.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-Smash-Balloon-300x153.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-Smash-Balloon-768x392.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smashballoon-instagram-feed/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram Feed</a> is a thoroughly responsive, fully customizable and SEO-friendly Instagram feed plugin that is super easy to setup and use. You can use it to display multiple Instagram feed on your website and customize each of them individually. </p>\n<p>It lets you combine your photos and videos in a single feed. Alongside, you can share your Instagram stories too with your audience. Stories can be displayed on a popup lightbox, so you can keep your visitors engaged for a long time.</p>\n<p>The plugin offers 3 different layout styles to display your pictures. Just like on Instagram, you can highlight your important feeds to let people know about your special moments. You can also tweak your pictures with the built-in customization option to give them the perfect look. Without a doubt, this plugin has been one of the most loved Instagram feeds plugins on the market.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https: