9/07/Instagram-Feed-by-WPDancers.jpg\" alt=\"Instagram Feed by WPDancers, \" width=\"775\" height=\"376\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234790\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-by-WPDancers.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-by-WPDancers-300x146.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-by-WPDancers-768x373.jpg 768w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Instagram-Feed-by-WPDancers-330x160.jpg 330w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/instagram-feed-wpdancers/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram Feed by WPDancers</a> is another brilliant plugin that you might want to check out. You can display your pictures in one of the 4 stylish layouts that the plugin offers &#8211; namely the Grid layout, Slide gallery, Polaroid layout, and the latest Map layout. The plugin also offers amazing real-time configurations. So you can select the transition style, the card skin, lightbox skin and a lot more.</p>\n<p>With the Moderate and Sleep options, you can control what to display on your site. You can use the toggle button to reject posts you do not want in your feed. The plugin also offers a range of beautiful skin options. That way you can select the one you like the best and integrate into your website for the best looks.</p>\n<p>The plugin also supports videos and allows you to add social share buttons. If you are not a fan of a very cluttered timeline, you can limit the number of posts that you want to display. The plugin exhibits super fast performance and is super flexible in terms of customization and design. Instagram Feed is overall easy to handle even if you&#8217;re using it for the first time. But if you still think that you need help, you can reach out to their friendly support team who is always ready to help you.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/modula-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >5. Modula</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/modula-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Modula.png\" alt=\"Modula Gallery plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"306\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234792\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Modula.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Modula-300x118.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Modula-768x303.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/modula-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Modula</a> is a WordPress Gallery plugin that allows you to display your photographs beautifully on your site. You can integrate it with various social media platforms too, including Instagram. With Modula, you can display media from your Instagram feed. The plugin offers fantastic filter options that you can use to improve the way your images look.</p>\n<p>With its drag and drop builder, you can customize your galleries quickly and easily. You can use it to resize your images and build your own custom layout. The plugin is super responsive which makes the images look crisp and clear on the screen size of all types. </p>\n<p>Modula also lets your visitors browse through your galleries by filtering them based on dates, hashtags, etc. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">6. NextGen Gallery</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nextgen-gallery.png\" alt=\"nextgen gallery\" width=\"775\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-217174\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nextgen-gallery.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nextgen-gallery-300x97.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nextgen-gallery-768x248.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/nextgen-gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">NextGen Gallery</a> is one of the most popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/\" title=\"8 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared\">gallery plugins for WordPress</a>. by purchasing one single plugin you can actually gain access to functions of more than 30 different extensions together. The plugin offers 10 different layout styles to display your pictures and has options for image sharing, image linking, commenting, and even proofing your images from being stolen.</p>\n<p>Then there are tons of beautiful options for your images. You can add filters, pick your favorite theme, and use the image Lightroom options. Best of all, this plugin provides you with lifetime updates and free support. This plugin is a great option for anyone who is looking for a way to showcase their Instagram pictures stunningly.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/instagram-widget/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">7. Instagram Widget by Elfsight</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/instagram-widget/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Elfsight.jpg\" alt=\"Elfsight\" width=\"775\" height=\"516\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234799\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Elfsight.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Elfsight-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Elfsight-768x511.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/instagram-widget/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram Widget</a> is yet another impressive plugin that lets you display your Instagram pictures on your website. You can use your hashtag or your username to add your pictures to your widget. The plugin is super flexible when it comes to customization. From adding colors, resizing your images to adding a scroll option, it comes with almost every Instagram integration feature you&#8217;ll need.</p>\n<p>It also responds very well to different gadgets and screen sizes. The plugin supports more than 16 different languages, so you can use this function to reach out and connect to more people. By adding the Follow button, you can encourage people to follow your site. This helps you attract more people and increase your fan base. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/feed-them-social/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">8. Feed Them Social</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/feed-them-social/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Feed-Them-Social.png\" alt=\"Feed Them Social, Instagram Plugins\" width=\"775\" height=\"362\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234803\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Feed-Them-Social.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Feed-Them-Social-300x140.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Feed-Them-Social-768x359.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/feed-them-social/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Feed Them Social</a> is a free WordPress plugin that comes loaded with amazing Instagram integration features. You can add any kind of social feed to your WordPress website, and display it in the most stylish manner. The feed can either be Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest or any other social media. The plugin is super easy to install, setup and use.</p>\n<p>With Feed Them Social, you can display your pictures either on your posts, pages or sidebar. You can also generate a shortcode using its shortcode generator in a matter of seconds. The customization option is vasts too. You have full freedom to style your site the way you want.</p>\n<p>You can change the color and font, add a Like or Follow button above or below your feed, and do a lot more. The plugin receives regular updates and is compatible with the latest versions of WordPress. So do check it out now. More than 70k people are already using it on their website. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/soliloquy/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">9. Soliloquy</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/soliloquy/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/soliloquy-review.png\" alt=\"Soliloquy\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224642\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/soliloquy-review.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/soliloquy-review-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/soliloquy-review-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/soliloquy/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Soliloquy</a> is an easy-to-use slider plugin for WordPress that lets you integrate your Instagram feed on your website sliders. With Soliloquy, you create featured content based on your posts, pages, and custom post types. It is also easy to create a lightbox slider to showcase your photos, videos, and galleries. </p>\n<p>You can even convert your PDFs and presentations to your sliders. The speed of the sliders can easily be controlled under the default settings. It is also possible that you schedule your sliders on your own timings. To protect your slider from being downloaded, you can disable the right click feature and ensure that your sliders are protected from theft or illegal use. </p>\n<p>The plugin is compatible with a lot of other advanced plugins too. The plugin is thoroughly responsive and looks stunning across platforms of all types.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smart-slider-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">10. Smart Slider 3</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smart-slider-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Smart-slider.png\" alt=\"Smart slider 3\" width=\"775\" height=\"369\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-234808\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Smart-slider.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Smart-slider-300x143.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Smart-slider-768x366.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/smart-slider-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Smart Slider 3</a> is another slider plugin that offers the best way to add your Instagram feed in the form of sliders on your website. But the plugin does not limit itself to letting you create sliders alone. You can also create beautiful carousels and blocks as well.</p>\n<p>This plugin also has a free version, which you can download from WordPress.org. Although the free one is good to go, the pro version promises to take your sliders to another level. You have 2 skin options &#8211; light and dark. It also has tons of effects that can be added to your pictures for an enhanced look.</p>\n<p>With Smart Slider 3, you can add as many as 11 layers to your website. That itself offers an added glamour to your website. You also have animation effects to make your sliders look unique. The plugin also comes with a lot of customization options.</p>\n<p>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/enjoy-instagram-instagram-responsive-images-gallery-and-carousel/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">11. Enjoy Instagram</a></h3>\n<p><a hre