es in the UK. But since there are so many web hosting options out there, it can be difficult to find the best choice for your website. </p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll go over the best UK web hosting. We’ll cover load time, uptime, support, pricing, and more so that you can choose the best web hosting for your UK site. </p>\n<h2>About Our UK Web Hosting Review Process</h2>\n<p>Before we get started with our picks for the best UK web hosting, let’s go over our review process. </p>\n<p>Since it’s not practical for you to sign up for numerous web hosts and test them all, we’ve done that for you for many of the most popular web hosts on this list. </p>\n<p>Here’s what we did to save you time and help you easily choose the best UK web hosting: </p>\n<ol>\n<li>Signed up with the best UK web hosts on the market. </li>\n<li>Created a test WordPress website. </li>\n<li>Mirrored a live site environment on those test sites by installing a WordPress theme as well as adding dummy content and images. </li>\n<li>Ran a few different speed tests to see how the site would perform and recorded the test data.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Now that you know how we reviewed these web hosts, let’s take a look at the #1 pick on our list for the best UK hosting. </p>\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >1. Bluehost</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bluehost-uk-1.jpg\" alt=\"bluehost-best-uk-web-hosting\" width=\"370\" height=\"194\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-234985\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bluehost-uk-1.jpg 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bluehost-uk-1-300x157.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 689 ms</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.99%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 9/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"http://isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with Bluehost &raquo;</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >Bluehost</a> is the most popular <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/\">web hosting provider</a>, powering over 2 million websites worldwide. Officially recommended by WordPress.org, Bluehost offers 1-click WordPress installation. So, you can start building your website in an instant, no complicated software to download and install. </p>\n<p>Each website hosted with Bluehost also comes with a free domain name and SSL certificate. Plus, you can try out Bluehost free for 30 days. If you don’t like their hosting service, they offer a money-back guarantee. </p>\n<p>Bluehost also offers 24/7 support, their trained in-house experts are available to help you out any time you need. In addition, they offer a help center that includes guides, video tutorials, and more. </p>\n<p><strong>UK Servers</strong>: Yes, London, UK. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Regular pricing starts at €6.29/month. </p>\n<p><strong>Special Offer</strong>: Our users pay €2.17/month (Over 60% off + free domain name, SSL). </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/bluehost-review/\">Read our Bluehost review &raquo;</a></p>\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >2. SiteGround</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/siteground-uk.jpg\" alt=\"siteground-uk-web-hosting\" width=\"370\" height=\"180\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-234986\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/siteground-uk.jpg 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/siteground-uk-300x146.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/siteground-uk-330x160.jpg 330w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 649 ms</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.98%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 10/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">SiteGround.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with SiteGround &raquo;</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/siteground/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >SiteGround</a> is another one of the most popular web hosting services and it’s recommended by many professional bloggers. They currently host 2 million domains. </p>\n<p>SiteGround offers reliable, fast, and secure web hosting for small and medium websites (sites that have 100,000 monthly visitors or fewer) and they provide best in class support. </p>\n<p>Plus, with a shared hosting plan you get a free website builder, free SSL certificate, free CloudFare CDN, free email accounts, as well as free daily backups. </p>\n<p><strong>UK Servers</strong>: Yes, London, UK. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Regular pricing starts at €9.95/month. </p>\n<p><strong>Special Offer</strong>: Our users get a special offer of €3.95/month. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/siteground-review/\">Read our full SiteGround review &raquo;</a></p>\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hostgator/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >3. HostGator</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/hostgator/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src