wp.com/hosting-reviews/hostgator-review/\">Read our HostGator review >></a></p>\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/a2hosting/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >4. A2 Hosting</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/a2hosting/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/a2-hosting-uk.jpg\" alt=\"a2-hosting-uk\" width=\"370\" height=\"174\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-234988\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/a2-hosting-uk.jpg 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/a2-hosting-uk-300x141.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 1.28 s</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.90%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 9/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: A2hosting.com</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/a2hosting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with A2 Hosting &raquo;</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/a2hosting/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >A2 Hosting</a> offers some of the fastest, easiest, most reliable web hosting for UK sites. Even the least expensive plan comes with 5 databases, unlimited storage, unlimited transfer, free SSL and SSD, an anytime money back guarantee, and more.</p>\n<p>With A2 Hosting, you also get access to their Turbo servers, which give you 20x faster loading pages. But, the Turbo servers are only available with the 2 priciest plans. </p>\n<p>A2 Hosting also comes with 2 operating systems, Windows and Linux, and you can install WordPress, Drupal, Joomla, and others with 1-click. </p>\n<p><strong>UK Servers</strong>: No, Amsterdam, Netherlands. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Regular pricing starts at €7.12/month. </p>\n<p><strong>Special Offer</strong>: Special offer pricing starts at only €2.64/month. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/a2-hosting-review/\">Read our A2 Hosting review >></a></p>\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >5. GreenGeeks</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" ><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/green-geeks.jpg\" alt=\"green-geeks-best-uk-web-host\" width=\"370\" height=\"186\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-234989\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/green-geeks.jpg 370w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/green-geeks-300x151.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Load time</strong>: 697 ms</li>\n<li><strong>Uptime</strong>: 99.92%</li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: 9/10</li>\n<li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">GreenGeeks.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"btn ltgreen light\">Get started with GreenGeeks &raquo;</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/greengeeks/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-nojs=\"true\" >GreenGeeks</a> is a green energy web hosting service that puts back 3x the power they consume into the grid in the form of green energy. Not only are they committed to the environment, but they provide the best speed technology, great security, and down-to-earth technical support. </p>\n<p>Each plan offers a 1-click app installer (including WordPress), unlimited web space, unlimited data transfer, free domain for the 1st year, free wildcard SSL, and more. </p>\n<p><strong>UK Servers</strong>: No, Amsterdam, Netherlands. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Regular pricing starts at $9.95/month (about €8.88/month). </p>\n<p><strong>Special Offer</strong>: Our users pay 