dget. But luckily, there&#8217;re tons of easy to use website builders that allow you to create professional websites without hiring a developer. [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/which-is-the-best-website-platform-for-small-business/\">Which Is the Best Website Platform for Small Business? (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20992:\"<p>Are you looking to create a website for your company? Want to know which is the best website platform for small business?</p>\n<p>Hiring a developer may be costly, especially if you&#8217;re on a budget. But luckily, there&#8217;re tons of easy to use website builders that allow you to create professional websites without hiring a developer. </p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll compare 6 best website builders for small business companies. </p>\n<h3>Choosing the Best Website Builder – What to Look For?</h3>\n<p>Choosing the best website builder is a crucial task because a better platform means more opportunities for growth. </p>\n<p>Here’re a few of the most important things to look for in a website builder. </p>\n<p><strong>1. Ease of Use</strong></p>\n<p>Ease of use is the most important thing to consider while choosing a website platform for your business. With a simple platform, you can quickly build and handle your website. This helps you to save time for more important tasks to grow your business.</p>\n<p><strong>2. Cost</strong></p>\n<p>The second most crucial factor to consider is the cost of creating a website and maintaining it. If you’re a small company with limited resources, then you need an affordable solution under your budget. </p>\n<p><strong>3. Scalability</strong></p>\n<p>As your website grows, you need more robust features and more resources. So, you need to check the scalability options while choosing a perfect website builder.</p>\n<p>With that said, let’s take a look at the best website builder platforms to make your website easily. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. WordPress.org</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wordpress-selfhosted.png\" alt=\"WordPress.org - Self-hosted WordPress Platform\" width=\"620\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-215604\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wordpress-selfhosted.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wordpress-selfhosted-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WordPress.org</a>, also known as the self-hosted WordPress, is the best website builder platform available on the market. Used by more than 30% of all websites, it’s the most popular website building software. </p>\n<p>Started as a simple blogging platform, WordPress has evolved to become the most powerful CMS (Content Management System) in existence today. It’s used by the world’s most popular blogs, largest brands, and business websites. </p>\n<p><strong>Creating a Website with WordPress:</strong></p>\n<p>Creating a website in WordPress looks somewhat technical at first; however, it’s not that hard. There’re tons of free resources on the internet that will guide you step by step. For example, you can see this guide on <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/guides/\" target=\"_blank\">how to make a WordPress website</a> by WPBeginner.   </p>\n<p>To build a website in WordPress, you need to install the WordPress software in your <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-hosting-services/\">web hosting</a> account first. If you choose a managed WordPress hosting like <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a>, it’ll be quick and easy because they have one-click WordPress installation option. </p>\n<p>After that, you can choose a WordPress theme for your website design. Next, you can install <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-plugins-and-tools-for-marketers/\">WordPress plugins</a> to add functionalities to your website. </p>\n<p>Once you’ve all the necessary tools installed, you can customize your website and publish it. </p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>WordPress is an open source website builder which gives you the maximum control and customization capabilities.</li>\n<li>There’re thousands of free and premium WordPress themes available to let you choose your website design. Similarly, there’re tons of free and paid WordPress plugins to let you add features and functionalities to your site.</li>\n<li>WordPress is SEO friendly by its design. Plus, there are awesome <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-seo-plugins-and-tools/\">WordPress SEO plugins</a> like <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yoast SEO</a> available to help you make your site search engine friendly.</li>\n<li>WordPress is highly scalable. You can easily integrate your WordPress site with third-party services like <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-email-newsletter-tools-compared-pros-and-cons/\">email marketing services</a>, payment services, etc. </li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>The responsibility of maintaining a WordPress site is fully yours. You need to keep it secure, maintain updates, etc. by yourself.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong></p>\n<p>WordPress is an open source free software, but need to purchase a <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/whats-the-difference-between-domain-and-hosting-beginners-guide/\">domain name and web hosting</a> plan to start a website. A domain name typically costs $14.99 / year, and a web hosting plan costs around $7.99 / month. </p>\n<p>But luckily, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> is offering our users a WordPress hosting plan for just $2.75 / month and a free domain name along with that. It means that you can start a WordPress website as low as $33 / year. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with WordPress.org on Bluehost!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/constant-contact-website-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Constant Contact Website Builder</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/constant-contact-website-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/constantcontactwebsitebuilder.png\" alt=\"Constant Contact Website Builder\" width=\"620\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-215605\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/constantcontactwebsitebuilder.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/constantcontactwebsitebuilder-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Constant Contact Website Builder is an artificial intelligence (A.I.) powered website builder. It allows you to create stunning custom websites within minutes. </p>\n<p><strong>Creating a Website with Constant Contact Website Builder:</strong></p>\n<p>Creating a business website with Constant Contact Website Builder is a simple and effortless process. You can simply sync your Facebook page, and then it’ll create a website using the information on your Facebook page. </p>\n<p>If you don’t have a Facebook page, then you’ll need to answer a few questions about the site you want to create. After that, it’ll do the rest. </p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Constant Contact Website Builder is simple and user-friendly. It allows you to easily create a website without using any code.</li>\n<li>The website builder takes care of your website security, speed, and offers you a peace of mind. It uses the super-fast content delivery network (CDN) to make your sites load faster.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Constant Contact</a> is the most popular <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-email-newsletter-tools-compared-pros-and-cons/\">email newsletter tools</a> on the market. The website builder with the powerful email marketing tool integration offers you great ways to optimize your site conversion.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Constant Contact Website Builder offers a free plan; however, it doesn’t allow you to use your domain name. If you want to have a custom domain, then you need to buy their paid plans which are expensive.</li>\n<li>Unlike WordPress, there aren’t any third-party tools and integrations available.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong></p>\n<p>Constant Contact Website Builder is a free website builder service. It provides a free Constant Contact subdomain to start a new site. </p>\n<p>If you want a custom domain name, then you need to upgrade to their paid plan. Their Starter plan costs $10 / month. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/constant-contact-website-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Constant Contact Website Builder today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/hostgator-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Gator Website Builder</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/hostgator-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/gatorwebsitebuilder.png\" alt=\"Gator Website Builder by HostGator\" width=\"620\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-215606\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/gatorwebsitebuilder.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/gatorwebsitebuilder-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As the name suggests, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/hostgator-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gator Website Builder</a> is a product of the popular domain and hosting company <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/hostgator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">HostGator</a>. Similar to Constant Contact Website Builder, Gator also allows you to create dynamic websites easily and quickly. </p>\n<p><strong>Creating a Website with Gator Website Builder:</strong></p>\n<p>Building a website with Gator Website Builder is a super easy task. Even a simple user without any technical skills can make a website using this platform. </p>\n<p>All you need to do is buy a Gator plan, choose a website template, and customize. It offers a simple drag and drop website builder interface, so you can quickly design a site. It allows you to easily edit and organize elements like text, columns, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\">contact forms</a>, and more. </p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>It’s a beginner-friendly website making platform. You can make a full-fledged business website, blog, or <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-woocommerce-store/\">online store</a> without any coding required.</li>\n<li>It’s a fully hosted platform, so you don’t need to worry about your website security, speed, updates, etc. </li>\n<li>There’re 200+ professional website templates available for use.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Gator Website Builder doesn’t offer any free plan or free trial. It means that you cannot test the builder before purchasing it.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong></p>\n<p>You can buy Gator Website Builder plans starting from $ 3.48 / month. The Premium Plan that offers priority support is available for $5.39 / month, and the eCommerce Plan for online store costs 8.30 / month.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/hostgator-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Gator Website Builder today!</a> </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bigcommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. BigCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bigcommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bigcommerce.png\" alt=\"BigCommerce Best eCommerce Website Builder\" width=\"620\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-215607\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bigcommerce.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/bigcommerce-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bigcommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">BigCommerce</a> is one of the most popular eCommerce website builders in the market. It provides a powerful and highly scalable eCommerce platform for building an online store. </p>\n<p><strong>Creating an Online Store with BigCommerce:</strong></p>\n<p>BigCommerce allows you to build a website in just a few steps. It features a three-step setup tool which asks you to enter your email address, and other details of the shop you want to make. Once you enter the details, it instantly creates a demo website for you. </p>\n<p>After that, you can configure the shop settings, and customize its design. There’re plenty of free and premium BigCommerce themes available, so you can pick one and start designing your store. </p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>BigCommerce is a perfect platform for users who want to build an eCommerce store with ease. It has simple interface along with powerful features to scale your business.</li>\n<li>BigCommerce lets you test its eCommerce site builder free for 15 days. You can sign up for the free trial without entering your credit card details.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>BigCommerce is a premium website maker service. There’s no free service available; however, you can try its interface free with the trial version.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong></p>\n<p>BigCommerce Plans are available for as low as $29.95 / month. If you want to use more powerful marketing tools, then you need to buy the Plus plan that costs $79.95 / month. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bigcommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with BigCommerce today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/wordpress-com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. WordPress.com</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/wordpress-com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wordpressdotcom.png\" alt=\"WordPress.com - Hosted Website Platform\" width=\"620\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-215610\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wordpressdotcom.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/wordpressdotcom-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/wordpress-com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WordPress.com</a> is the fully hosted version of WordPress. It’s a subscription-based website building service run by the co-founder of the WordPress software.</p>\n<p>Unlike WordPress.org, WordPress.com is a fully managed website platform which provides you the whole package of hosting and other software. </p>\n<p><strong>Creating a Website with WordPress.com:</strong></p>\n<p>Like all the other website builders, WordPress.com also lets you make a website in some easy steps. To get started, you just need to enter your email address, provide some details about the site you want to build. </p>\n<p>It offers a step by step setup wizard to guide you through the whole process. During the process, you can choose your website type; a blog or business site, or an eCommerce store. After that, it provides you with a suitable subdomain, themes, and other tools. </p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>It’s is easy and quick to make a website with WordPress.com. You don’t need to look for a web hosting service and other growth tools because it offers them all.</li>\n<li>WordPress.com also takes care of updates, backup, security, and speed of your site so that you can have peace of mind.</li>\n<li>It has plenty of themes and templates available for use. You can choose a theme of your choice and make a design like you want.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>WordPress.com doesn’t allow you to install custom plugins. With a paid plan, you can install additional plugins, however, it has strict rules for third-party services.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong></p>\n<p>You can create a website or blog free at WordPress.com; however, it has limited features. If you want to use a custom domain name, then you need to purchase their paid plans.</p>\n<p>The Blogger plan lets you use a .blog domain for $3 / month. You need to buy their Personal plan for $5 / month to use a custom domain. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/wordpress-com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with WordPress.com today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.squarespace.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Squarespace</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.squarespace.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/squarespace.png\" alt=\"Squarespace - Simple Website Building Platform\" width=\"620\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-215609\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/squarespace.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/squarespace-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Similar to WordPress.com, <a href=\"https://www.squarespace.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Squarespace</a> is also a fully hosted website platform. It allows you to create a professional website, portfolio, or an online store within minutes. </p>\n<p>Squarespace offers powerful website building tools for all types of websites. You can use it to create sites for small businesses, entrepreneurs, photographers, restaurants, musicians, and more. </p>\n<p><strong>Creating a Website with Squarespace:</strong></p>\n<p>Similar to Constant Contact Website Builder, Squarespace also comes with artificial intelligence (A.I.) powered website builder for you. You need to answer a few questions, and then it’ll create a site for you. </p>\n<p>Alternately, it also allows you to design your website by choosing a template. </p>\n<p><strong>Pros:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Squarespace comes with a simple drag and drop website editor. You just need to click on any element to start editing that element.</li>\n<li>It offers a 15 day free trial for testing purpose. You can use the Squarespace platform free for 15 days without providing your credit card details.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Cons:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>It has limited integrations with third-party services and payment providers.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong></p>\n<p>Squarespace pricing plans start from $12 / month. Their most popular Business plan costs $18 / month. </p>\n<h3>Which Website Builder Platform You Should Use?</h3>\n<p>After reviewing the best website builders for small business, we’ve come to the conclusion that <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WordPress.org</a> is the best overall website builder. It offers limitless design options and growth possibilities with plugins and integrations. </p>\n<p>But if you want an AI-powered website builder, then <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/constant-contact-website-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Constant Contact Website Builder</a> is the best choice for you. It allows you to make a website without any hassle. </p>\n<p>Also, it&#8217;s the best free website builder for users looking for a free solution. </p>\n<p>If you want to create an eCommerce store, then <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/bigcommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">BigCommerce</a> is the perfect choice for you. It provides you with a simple interface as well as powerful tools to grow your online sales. </p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to find the best website platform for small business. You may also want to see our guide on best <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/ecommerce-email-marketing-best-practices-to-grow-sales/\">eCommerce email marketing practices to grow sales</a>. </p>\n<p>And don’t forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more helpful website making and growth tips.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\