:\"WooCommerce Marketing\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/?p=191096\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:656:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WooCommerce plugins and extensions for your online store? WooCommerce is the official plugin for building an eCommerce site in WordPress. However, it doesn’t include all the advanced features you’ll need to run a full-fledged online shop on its own. That’s where WooCommerce plugins and extensions come in handy. There’re [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-woocommerce-plugins-and-extensions/\">24 Best WooCommerce Plugins to Grow Your Traffic and Sales (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34328:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WooCommerce plugins and extensions for your online store? <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WooCommerce</a> is the official plugin for building an eCommerce site in WordPress. However, it doesn’t include all the advanced features you’ll need to run a full-fledged online shop on its own.</p>\n<p>That’s where WooCommerce plugins and extensions come in handy. There’re tons of powerful plugins and tools available to add useful features to your <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-woocommerce-store/\">WooCommerce store</a>, and help boost your sales.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the 24 best WooCommerce plugins and extensions to grow your eCommerce store faster.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">1. MonsterInsights</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-186638\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/monsterinsightsbestgapluginforwordpress.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights Best Google Analytics Plugin for WordPress\" width=\"620\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/monsterinsightsbestgapluginforwordpress.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/monsterinsightsbestgapluginforwordpress-300x155.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">MonsterInsights</a> is the most popular Google Analytics plugin for WordPress. It tracks your eCommerce site visitors’ online behavior and provides you with detailed reports on exactly how they’re interacting with your store.</p>\n<p>The plugin comes with a powerful <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/addon/ecommerce/\">eCommerce addon</a> for tracking the performance of your WordPress stores. It lets you easily <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-track-ecommerce-sales-in-google-analytics/\"> track your eCommerce sales</a>. Some of the key eCommerce reports include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-find-your-most-popular-ecommerce-products-in-google-analytics/\">Most Popular eCommerce Products in your store</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-find-your-average-ecommerce-order-value-in-google-analytics/\">Average eCommerce Order Value</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/which-traffic-source-generates-the-most-revenue/\">Traffic source that generates the most revenue</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/google-analytics-lifetime-value-report-for-woocommerce/\"> Lifetime value of your WooCommerce shop</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/google-analytics-lifetime-value-report-for-woocommerce/\">Individual WooCommerce customer tracking</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Once you have all these important reports in hand, you can make data-driven decisions to boost your WooCommerce sales.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">2. OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155241\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software.jpg\" alt=\"optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software\" width=\"560\" height=\"260\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software-300x139.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">OptinMonster</a> is the most powerful, most popular lead generation software available on the market. It helps you convert your website visitors into subscribers to grow your email list faster.</p>\n<p>OptinMonster comes with highly effective features including its signature feature, <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/features/exit-intent/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Exit-intent technology</a>. It&#8217;s a smart behavioral technology that monitors the movement of your site visitors and prompts them with a targeted campaign at the exact moment they&#8217;re about to exit your site.</p>\n<p>You can use this feature to reduce cart abandonment and increase sales in your WooCommerce store.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-wishlist/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">3. YITH WooCommerce Wishlist</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-wishlist/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191101\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommercewishlist.png\" alt=\"YITH WooCommerce Wishlist Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommercewishlist.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommercewishlist-300x140.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-wishlist/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YITH WooCommerce Wishlist</a> is a cool WooCommerce extension plugin to improve the user experience and indirect sales of your store.</p>\n<p>The plugin allows shoppers to create a wishlist of the products they want to buy. This is useful during the holiday season when people are making shopping lists and buying gifts.</p>\n<p>Also, visitors can share their wishlist via email or social media. This helps to increase your sales indirectly as friends and relatives of your customers use the list to buy .</p>\n<h3><a href=\"ttps://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">4. WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"ttps://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-158461\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin-300x121.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"ttps://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">WPForms</a> is a simple drag and drop form builder plugin for WordPress. It allows you to create a variety of online forms, including advanced forms like <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-survey-in-wordpress/\">surveys</a> and <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/plugins/how-to-create-conversational-forms-in-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">conversational forms</a>, easily without using any code.</p>\n<p>With WPForms, you can quickly build a beautiful contact form page for your online store. When your users/customers want to ask you anything, they can contact you via your contact page.</p>\n<p>Besides, you can create surveys and quizzes to improve your user engagement. Conversational surveys also offer a fun way to collect user feedback about your products.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://yoast.com/wordpress/plugins/yoast-woocommerce-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">5. Yoast WooCommerce SEO Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://yoast.com/wordpress/plugins/yoast-woocommerce-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-124474\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/WooCommerce-Marketing-Tools-Yoast-WooCommerce-SEO.2.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Marketing Tools - Yoast WooCommerce SEO\" width=\"560\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/WooCommerce-Marketing-Tools-Yoast-WooCommerce-SEO.2.png 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/WooCommerce-Marketing-Tools-Yoast-WooCommerce-SEO.2-300x155.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you want your website to be found in search results, you need to focus on your site’s SEO.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re already using the popular <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yoast-premium/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yoast SEO </a>plugin, you might want to check out the “glue” that holds WooCommerce and your SEO plugin together, <a href=\"https://yoast.com/wordpress/plugins/yoast-woocommerce-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WooCommerce SEO</a>.</p>\n<p>Not only does this marketing tool optimize your website like the free Yoast SEO plugin, but it also takes things one step further and optimizes it for WooCommerce itself. This gives your marketing efforts the push needed to get ahead of the competition.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Share products on Pinterest as Rich Pins for a better viewing and sharing experience</li>\n<li>Exclude unnecessary information on your shop’s sitemap that may get in the way of proper indexing and search rankings</li>\n<li>Utilize the breadcrumbs feature, which is better than the default WooCommerce option</li>\n<li>Never forget to optimize for WooCommerce in the edit page because it comes before anything else</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking to maximize your SEO efforts you might want to consider investing in this SEO plugin.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-product-reviews-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">6. WooCommerce Product Reviews Pro</a></h3>\n<p>Claiming that 70% of your customers will view a review before finalizing their purchase, the team at WooCommerce created an extension that allows you to accept product reviews from customers, complete with images and video.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommerceproductreviewsplugin.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Product Reviews Plugin\" width=\"550\" height=\"337\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214304\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommerceproductreviewsplugin.png 550w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommerceproductreviewsplugin-300x184.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-product-reviews-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WooCommerce Product Reviews Pro</a> also lets your customers filter reviews by star ratings, flag reviews that need moderation, upvote or downvote reviews, and boost user interaction. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/affiliate-royale/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Affiliate Royale</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/affiliate-royale/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/affiliateroyale.png\" alt=\"Affiliate Royale Best WordPress Affiliate Program Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-212250\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/affiliateroyale.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/affiliateroyale-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/affiliate-royale/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Affiliate Royale</a> is a powerful affiliate program plugin for WordPress. It comes with seamless integration with WooCommerce that you can create and run a full-fledged affiliate program on your WooCommerce store. </p>\n<p>This WooCommerce affiliate marketing solution helps boost traffic, rank your store higher in search results, and generate more revenue as others promote your online shop for you.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-multilingual/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">8. WooCommerce Multilingual</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-multilingual/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191105\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercemultilingual.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Multilingual plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"205\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercemultilingual.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercemultilingual-300x99.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-multilingual/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WooCommerce Multilingual</a> is a translation management plugin for WooCommerce. It comes as an extension of the WPML WordPress Multilingual plugin for WooCommerce-based websites.</p>\n<p>It helps you to translate your WooCommerce products, categories, and everything throughout the checkout process into the language of your choice. You can also send emails to clients and admins in the same language.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-points-and-rewards/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">9. WooCommerce Points and Rewards</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-points-and-rewards/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercepointsrewardsplugin.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Points and Rewards Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214306\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercepointsrewardsplugin.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercepointsrewardsplugin-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Rewarding loyal customers is a great way to encourage them to refer their friends and family, write a positive review, or sign up for your email list. And the great thing is, this helps with WooCommerce automation because your customers do all the work for you.</p>\n<p>WooCommerce Points and Rewards is a WooCommerce extension plugin which lets you provide loyalty points to your customers which they can redeem for discounts. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/recommendation-engine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow rel= noopener\">10. WooCommerce Recommendation Engine</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/recommendation-engine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow rel= noopener\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercereceommendationengineplugin.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Recommendation Engine Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"356\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214307\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercereceommendationengineplugin.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercereceommendationengineplugin-300x172.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you really want to boost the number of sales you generate on your site, use this <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/recommendation-engine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow rel= noopener\">product recommendation extension </a>and start showing customers related products they may be interested in. </p>\n<p>Base the recommendations on purchase history, product views, what others have viewed, and what is often bundled and purchased together.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-ajax-search/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">11. YITH WooCommerce Ajax Search</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-ajax-search/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191106\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommerceajaxsearch.png\" alt=\"YITH WooCommerce Ajax Search\" width=\"620\" height=\"291\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommerceajaxsearch.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommerceajaxsearch-300x141.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-ajax-search/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YITH WooCommerce Ajax Search</a> plugin helps your customers to find what they’re looking for in your store quickly. Instead of browsing across the entire store, they can search for a product they want and buy it instantly.</p>\n<p>The plugin displays search results immediately as users start typing a product name in the search field. It&#8217;s super fast and highly efficient.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-products-slider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">12. PP WooCommerce Products Slider</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-products-slider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191109\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommerceproductslider.png\" alt=\"PP WooCommerce Product Slider\" width=\"620\" height=\"205\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommerceproductslider.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommerceproductslider-300x99.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-products-slider/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">PP WooCommerce Products Slider</a> lets you create beautiful sliders to display your products in eye-catching new ways. You can add your best products to the product sliders and carousels to instantly visually engage your users.</p>\n<p>Using the plugin, you can create as many sliders as you want and show them anywhere on your website.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-compare/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">13. YITH WooCommerce Compare</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-compare/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191110\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yithwoocommercecompare.png\" alt=\"YITH WooCommerce Compare Pllugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yithwoocommercecompare.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yithwoocommercecompare-300x140.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-compare/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YITH WooCommerce Compare</a> plugin lets your users compare 2 or more products side-by-side so they can make informed buying decisions.</p>\n<p>Often, shoppers cannot decide which product to buy as they find multiple products of the same nature. At such times of confusion, this simple comparison feature helps them quickly find out which product best suits their needs.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yith-woocommerce-gift-cards/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">14. YITH WooCommerce Gift Cards</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yith-woocommerce-gift-cards/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191112\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yithwoocommercegiftcards.png\" alt=\"YITH WooCommerce Gift Cards Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yithwoocommercegiftcards.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yithwoocommercegiftcards-300x140.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yith-woocommerce-gift-cards/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YITH WooCommerce Gift Cards</a> allows your users to purchase gift cards of any amount and send them to their friends and relatives as a gift. The gift cards are prepaid vouchers which will enable their recipients to buy things from your store.</p>\n<p>With gift cards, your customers have a low stress option to show others they care. They won&#8217;t have to deal with the anxiety and confusion of picking out a specific product. On the other hand, the gift card recipients can now buy a product of their choice. Everyone wins!</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woocommerce-discount-rules/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">15. Discount Rules for WooCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woocommerce-discount-rules/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191113\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/discountrulesforwoocommerce.png\" alt=\"Discount Rules for WooCommerce Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"214\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/discountrulesforwoocommerce.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/discountrulesforwoocommerce-300x104.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Discounts are one of the best ways to boost user interest and increase sales. Because everyone loves getting a deal, you can ultimately sell more by offering discounts.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woocommerce-discount-rules/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Discount Rules for WooCommerce</a> allows you to create dynamic pricing and discounts in your WooCommerce store easily. You can offer a store-wide global discount, cart discounts, special offers, and more with this plugin.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-pdf-invoices-packing-slips/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">16. WooCommerce PDF Invoices &amp; Packing Slips</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-pdf-invoices-packing-slips/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191114\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercepdfinvoices.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce PDF Invoices and Packing Slips\" width=\"620\" height=\"202\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercepdfinvoices.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woocommercepdfinvoices-300x98.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-pdf-invoices-packing-slips/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WooCommerce PDF Invoices &amp; Packing Slips</a> is a free extension for WooCommerce. It automatically adds a PDF invoice to the order confirmation emails sent out to your customers.</p>\n<p>It also makes the PDF invoices and packing slips available in your customer’s account area. They can easily download or print them from there.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-quick-view/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">17. YITH WooCommerce Quick View</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-quick-view/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191115\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommerce-quick-view.png\" alt=\"YITH WooCommeerce Quick View Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommerce-quick-view.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommerce-quick-view-300x140.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-quick-view/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YITH WooCommerce Quick View</a> allows you to add a quick view option for WooCommerce products. A quick view lets your customers see a product&#8217;s details instantly with a click or a mouse hover.</p>\n<p>This feature saves your customers’ time by not having to open and load a new page for each product that piques their curiosity. It improves user experience and helps to boost your store&#8217;s sales.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">18. YITH WooCommerce Request a Quote</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191117\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommercerequestaquote.png\" alt=\"YITH WooCommerce Request a Quote Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommercerequestaquote.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/yith-woocommercerequestaquote-300x140.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>One of the disadvantages of online shopping is the lack of negotiation, but that will no longer be an issue with <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">YITH WooCommerce Request a Quote</a> plugin.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s a WooCommerce extension plugin by YITH which allows you to add a ‘Quote Request’ button to your store. Using the button, your customers can send a quote request to you for price negotiation.</p>\n<p>This is useful when your customers want to buy large quantities of the same product, and they want a discount on the price. The plugin enables negotiation option for bulk buyers.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/google-product-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">19. Google Product Feed</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/google-product-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/gproductfeedwoocommerceextension.png\" alt=\"Google Product Feed WooCommerce Extension\" width=\"620\" height=\"356\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-214310\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/gproductfeedwoocommerceextension.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/gproductfeedwoocommerceextension-300x172.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Google Product Feed plugin lets you create a real-time feed of your WooCommerce store’s products and services to the Google Merchant Center as a unique way of advertising. </p>\n<p>In fact, this extension automates the entire process of feeding product information to Google. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mailchimp-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">20. MailChimp for WooCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mailchimp-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191104\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/mailchimpforwoocommerce.png\" alt=\"MailChimp for WooCommerce plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"219\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/mailchimpforwoocommerce.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/mailchimpforwoocommerce-300x106.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>MailChimp is one of the most popular email marketing services available on the market. Their official WooCommerce plugin is <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/mailchimp-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">MailChimp for WooCommerce</a>.</p>\n<p>When installed on your WooCommerce website, the plugin automatically syncs your customers and their purchase data with your MailChimp account. Then, you can send targeted email campaigns to them and make more sales.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woomarketing-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">21. WooMarketing Bundle</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woomarketing-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191118\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-marketing-bundle.png\" alt=\"WooMarketing Bundle Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"286\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-marketing-bundle.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-marketing-bundle-300x138.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As its name suggests, <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woomarketing-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">WooMarketing Bundle</a> is a package of WooCommerce marketing extensions. It&#8217;s an official plugin from the WooCommerce team themselves.</p>\n<p>The bundle plugin includes email marketing, Facebook Ads integration, smarter discounts, transactional emails, social logins, etc.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s an excellent offer if you want to implement all the marketing features included in it. Because buying separate plugins for each feature would cost you a lot more than purchasing this single plugin.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woocommerce-pack-and-ship-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">22. WooCommerce Pack &amp; Ship Bundle</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/woocommerce-pack-and-ship-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191119\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-pack-and-ship-bundle.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Pack and Ship Bundle\" width=\"620\" height=\"286\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-pack-and-ship-bundle.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/woo-pack-and-ship-bundle-300x138.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WooCommerce Pack &amp; Ship Bundle is a complete package plugin that enables you to sell, pack, and ship products worldwide. It&#8217;s also an official plugin from Team WooCommerce.</p>\n<p>The plugin comes with powerful features including responsive 360-degree image rotation, invoices, packing lists, product kits, multi-address shipping and tracking, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://hootsuite.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">23. Hootsuite</a></h3>\n<p>Utilizing the power of social media can expand your brand to a wider customer base and bring more traffic to your WooCommerce shop.</p>\n<p>However, running an online shop requires a lot of work. From administrative tasks to fulfilling orders, there&#8217;s not a lot of time to promote your company the way you want to.</p>\n<p>That’s where <a href=\"https://hootsuite.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Hootsuite</a> comes in handy.</p>\n<p>In fact, Hootsuite helps with WooCommerce marketing automation by allowing you to schedule your social media posts in advance on up to 30 different social media platforms.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-124458\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/WooCommerce-Marketing-Tools-Hootsuite.png\" alt=\"WooCommerce Marketing Tools - Hootsuite\" width=\"560\" height=\"385\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/WooCommerce-Marketing-Tools-Hootsuite.png 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/WooCommerce-Marketing-Tools-Hootsuite-300x206.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>Not only does this save you time, but it also helps you gain more leads that can convert into sales.</p>\n<p>Not to mention you can communicate directly with your team in the Hootsuite dashboard, view detailed analytics reports, and use pre-written responses, automating your marketing process even more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/product-import-export-for-woo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">24. Product Import Export for WooCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/product-import-export-for-woo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-191121\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/productimportexportpluginforwoocommerce.png\" alt=\"Product Import Export for WooCommerce\" width=\"620\" height=\"205\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/productimportexportpluginforwoocommerce.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/productimportexportpluginforwoocommerce-300x99.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/product-import-export-for-woo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Product Import Export for WooCommerce</a> allows you to import or export simple products in CSV format. If you need to send your product details to someone, the export feature comes in handy.</p>\n<p>Using this plugin, you can bulk upload and update products in your WooCommerce store. Hence, you don’t need to enter data for every single product manually.</p>\n<p>So, that’s it! The list of the 24 best WooCommerce plugins and extensions for maximizing your WooCommerce store revenue. We hope this article helped you to choose the plugins most useful for your website.</p>\n<p>You might also want to check out our list of the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-plugins-and-tools-for-marketers/\">best WordPress plugins for every website</a> (free + premium).</p>\n<p>Also, don’t forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more WooCommerce guides and Google Analytics tutorials.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-woocommerce-plugins-and-extensions/\">24 Best WooCommerce Plugins to Grow Your Traffic and Sales (2019)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-woocommerce-plugins-and-extensions/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"7 Best WordPress LMS Plugins: Which Is Best for You?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:129:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-lms-plugins/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=best-wordpress-lms-plugins\";s:7:\"attribs