-wordpress-plugin-300x96.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/broken-link-checker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Broken Link Checker</a> is one of the most user-friendly WordPress plugins ever made. </p>\n<p>Just as its name says, Broken Link Checker is a plugin that monitors your site for broken links and missing images. If it detects any broken links or missing images, it immediately notifies you so you can instantly fix them.</p>\n<p>Furthermore, it can make broken links display differently in posts and prevent search engines from following such links. Thus, the plugin saves you from negative SEO rankings.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/broken-link-checker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Broken Link Checker today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"reviveoldposts\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">31. Revive Old Posts &#8211; Must-have Social Media Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-162113\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revive-old-post-wordpress-p.jpg\" alt=\"revive-old-post-wordpress-p\" width=\"620\" height=\"198\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revive-old-post-wordpress-p.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revive-old-post-wordpress-p-300x96.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a><br />\nSocial media marketing is a comparatively new component in the digital marketing world, but it&#8217;s a very effective one. It’s a way of engaging the huge social media audience with your marketing content.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Revive Old Posts</a> is an incredible plugin for social media marketing and <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-content-marketing-plugins-and-tools-for-wordpress/\">content marketing</a>. The plugin helps you engage people on social media with your old WordPress posts. You can automatically share your old WordPress articles using this plugin and drive traffic to your site.</p>\n<p>The plugin allows you to choose the time between posts and the number of posts to share to make it organized. Plus, you can use hashtags to focus on topics.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Revive Old Posts today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"inlinerelatedposts\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/intelly-related-posts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">32. Inline Related Posts &#8211; Cool Content Optimization Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/intelly-related-posts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-162129\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/inline-related-posts-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"inline-related-posts-plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"198\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/inline-related-posts-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/inline-related-posts-plugin-300x96.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/intelly-related-posts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Inline Related Posts</a> plugin helps you enhance user engagement on your WordPress posts by displaying related content inside your articles. Most websites show related content after the end of articles due to which users need to scroll down the whole article to see the related content. But people can exit your post anywhere in-between if they don’t find it useful.</p>\n<p>So, the plugin can help you to keep your visitors on site by displaying related posts. If they see the relevant content more useful, they can switch to that post instead of leaving your site. This technique is especially helpful for long articles.</p>\n<p>This is a very simple-yet-interesting marketing strategy which can improve user engagement on your WordPress blogs.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/intelly-related-posts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Inline Related Posts today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"quickeasyfaqs\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quick-and-easy-faqs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">33. Quick and Easy FAQs &#8211; Best FAQ Management Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quick-and-easy-faqs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-162131\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quick-and-easy-faqs-wordpress-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"quick-and-easy-faqs-wordpress-plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"198\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quick-and-easy-faqs-wordpress-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quick-and-easy-faqs-wordpress-plugin-300x96.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Frequently asked questions (FAQs) are widely used on websites to answer common questions. By adding the FAQ section on your site, you can solve several queries your site visitors want to ask without having to manually reply to each visitor.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quick-and-easy-faqs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Quick and Easy FAQs</a> is a free WordPress plugin that makes it easy to create beautiful FAQs in WordPress. You can display the FAQs in different styles like simple list style, toggle style, filterable toggle, etc.</p>\n<p>In short, this plugin helps you to improve communication and increase your conversions.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/quick-and-easy-faqs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Quick and Easy FAQs today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"easygooglefonts\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-google-fonts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">34. Easy Google Fonts &#8211; Best Googe Fonts WordPress Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-google-fonts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-154158\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/easy-google-fonts-free-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"easy-google-fonts-free-plugin\" width=\"560\" height=\"182\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/easy-google-fonts-free-plugin.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/easy-google-fonts-free-plugin-300x98.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Typography is one of the significant aspects of good design. If your theme doesn’t have cool fonts, your website design may not be eye-catching enough to maintain your visitors&#8217; interests.</p>\n<p>However, you can use the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-google-fonts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Easy Google Fonts</a> plugin and solve this problem easily. It’s a free plugin that lets you use 600+ Google fonts on your WordPress site. Using this plugin is easy; no coding is required. Even a beginner can effortlessly configure the plugin and add beautiful fonts in WordPress.</p>\n<p>The plugin uses a live customizer so that you can preview fonts in real-time as you make changes.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/easy-google-fonts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Easy Google Fonts today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"loginlockdown\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/login-lockdown/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">35. Login Lockdown &#8211; Useful WordPress Security Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/login-lockdown/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-154159\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/login-lockdown-free-wp-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"login-lockdown-free-wp-plugin\" width=\"560\" height=\"182\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/login-lockdown-free-wp-plugin.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/login-lockdown-free-wp-plugin-300x98.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Although you set a strong username and password to access your WordPress dashboard, it can sometimes fall prey to brute force password discovery. So, you’ll need to use the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/login-lockdown/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Login Lockdown</a> plugin to protect your site from such attacks.</p>\n<p>It records the IP address and timestamp for every failed login attempt. If it detects more than a set number of failed login attempts, it disables the login function for that user for a specified period.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s an essential WordPress plugin to keep your website secure. </p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/login-lockdown/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Login Lockdown today!</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"duplicator\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/duplicator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">36. Duplicator &#8211; Best WordPress Migration Plugin</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/duplicator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-154161\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/duplicator-free-wordpress-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"duplicator-free-wordpress-plugin\" width=\"560\" height=\"182\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/duplicator-free-wordpress-plugin.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/duplicator-free-wordpress-plugin-300x98.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/duplicator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Duplicator</a>, as its name suggests, helps you to duplicate your website data. It’s useful when you need to move your website data from one location to another, like moving to a new host. This is also helpful for creating site backups.</p>\n<p>Using Duplicator, you can clone the live site data and install it on localhost for moving your site. Then, with the help of localhost data, you can move your site to a new web host without downtime.</p>\n<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Free. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/duplicator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Get started with Duplicator today!</a></p>\n<p>Before wrapping it up, here&#8217;s what we have promised above! </p>\n<h3 id=\"chooseplugin\">How to Choose the Best WordPress Plugin for Your Website?</h3>\n<p>WordPress plugins let you add extra functionality to improve your website design, marketing, and a variety of other aspects related to growth. </p>\n<p>However, WordPress beginners cannot find the best plugins because they don&#8217;t know how to choose them. Here&#8217;re some simple tips you can use to find the best WordPress plugins. </p>\n<p><strong>1. User Reviews and Ratings</strong></p>\n<p>User reviews and ratings give you plenty of idea on how the plugin works in reality. And, you can rely on them because they&#8217;re the actual experiences of the plugin users. </p>\n<p>You can find WordPress plugin reviews and ratings in the sidebar area on the official WordPress.org plugin pages. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wppluginreviews.png\" alt=\"WordPress Plugins Review to Choose the Best WordPress Plugins\" width=\"620\" height=\"365\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-208799\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wppluginreviews.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/wppluginreviews-300x177.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>You can view full reviews by clicking on the &#8216;See all&#8217; link in the Rating section.  </p>\n<p>For example, our plugin <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-analytics-for-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\">MonsterInsights</a> has received 808 five-star ratings out of 1035 total reviews. The best part is that all the recent reviews are five-star ratings. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/miratingsandreviews.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights Plugin Reviews and Ratings\" width=\"620\" height=\"443\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-208803\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/miratingsandreviews.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/miratingsandreviews-300x214.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2. Customer Support</strong></p>\n<p>Customer support is another crucial thing to consider while choosing the best plugins for WordPress. You need a plugin that provides you instant support whenever you need it. </p>\n<p>For official WordPress plugins, you can view the support forum in WordPress.org. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/misupportforum.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights Support Forum\" width=\"620\" height=\"355\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-208805\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/misupportforum.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/misupportforum-300x172.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>For example, the MonsterInsights support forum has all the questions already solved (the tick mark).</p>\n<p><strong>3. Plugin Screenshots</strong></p>\n<p>Plugin screenshots let you see how the plugin interface looks in the backend and frontend. You need a simple interface to work efficiently. </p>\n<p>You can find the plugin screenshots in the WordPress.org Plugin pages. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mipluginscreenshots.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights Plugin Screenshots\" width=\"620\" height=\"447\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-208808\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mipluginscreenshots.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mipluginscreenshots-300x216.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>That&#8217;s it! </p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best WordPress plugins and tools to grow your business website fast in 2019. You may also want to check out our list of <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-hosting-services/\">best WordPress hosting services 2019</a>.</p>\n<p>Also, don’t forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more useful WordPress tutorials.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-plugins-and-tools-for-marketers/\">35+ Best WordPress Plugins 2019 (Grow Your Website FASTER!)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xm