;s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"social proof examples\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/?p=208732\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:661:\"<p>Are you looking for the best social proof WordPress plugins for your website? Social proof is any content which shows that your services are socially approved, trusted, and used by people. Using social proof on your website helps to increase trust for your company and boosts your sales. That’s why big brands like Amazon and [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-social-proof-wordpress-plugins-to-boost-your-sales/\">7 Best WordPress Plugins &#038; Tools to Add Social Proof and Boost Your Sales [2019]</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Sunita Rai\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16306:\"<p>Are you looking for the best social proof WordPress plugins for your website? Social proof is any content which shows that your services are socially approved, trusted, and used by people. </p>\n<p>Using social proof on your website helps to increase trust for your company and boosts your sales. That’s why big brands like Amazon and many others are using social proof on their site. </p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll share with you 7 best social proof WordPress plugins 2019 to boost your sales. </p>\n<h3>What is Social Proof? + Social Proof Examples</h3>\n<p>Social proof is a psychological phenomenon where people rely on the actions of others to decide what is right and what is wrong. </p>\n<p>It is a type of conformity that people use at ambiguous times – they observe what others are doing and copy the same behavior. It assumes that people perceive group behavior as appropriate behavior. </p>\n<p>Marketers have long been using this principle as a tactic to gain the trust of new consumers. </p>\n<p>Some of the most popular social proof examples in use are testimonials, customer reviews, celebrity brand endorsements, certifications, and various stats.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/customertestimonials.png\" alt=\"Customer Testimonials as Social Proof\" width=\"620\" height=\"266\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210796\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/customertestimonials.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/customertestimonials-300x129.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>Here is a simple example: Users come to your website and think of buying your product, but they cannot decide because they don’t trust you. But if you have added a testimonial from a known industry expert next to the purchase button, then they’re more likely to trust and buy your product. </p>\n<p>With that said, let’s take a look at the best WordPress social proof plugins you can use to grow your sales and revenue. </p>\n<h3>Best Social Proof Marketing Plugins for WordPress (2019)</h3>\n<h3><a href=\"https://trustpulse.com/\" target=\"_blank\">1. TrustPulse</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://trustpulse.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/trustpulsebestsocialproofapp.png\" alt=\"TrustPulse Best Social Proof App for WordPress\" width=\"620\" height=\"297\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210785\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/trustpulsebestsocialproofapp.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/trustpulsebestsocialproofapp-300x144.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://trustpulse.com/\" target=\"_blank\">TrustPulse</a> is the most powerful social proof app for business websites. It helps to increase trust, conversions, and sales by displaying attractive social proof notifications on your website. </p>\n<p>It allows you to track purchases, downloads, or registrations on your website, and show them as a recent activity or a count of events. You can choose exactly where and when to display notifications to convert more users into customers. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/trustpulse-social-proof-notification.png\" alt=\"A social proof notification by TrustPulse\" width=\"560\" height=\"222\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-210862\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/trustpulse-social-proof-notification.png 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/trustpulse-social-proof-notification-300x119.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>TrustPulse also works as a FOMO (fear of missing out) plugin as it creates a feeling of urgency with swift notifications. </p>\n<p>This social proof app works well on all <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/best-website-builders-for-small-business-compared-pros-and-cons/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">popular website platforms</a>, including WordPress, Shopify, Squarespace, Drupal, and more. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://trustpulse.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get started with TrustPulse today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">2. WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"WPForms Best WordPress Form Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"250\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-158461\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-wordpress-form-builder-plugin-300x121.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Customer reviews are among the most powerful social proof elements you can use on your website. </p>\n<p>As user reviews are actual experiences of the real users, consumers find them more trustworthy. According to a study, consumers are 92% more likely to trust their peers over advertising. </p>\n<p>In WordPress, you can easily collect customer reviews and display them on your website using the <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WPForms</a> plugin. </p>\n<p>WPForms is the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\">most user-friendly WordPress form plugin</a> which lets you create simple to advanced forms easily and quickly. It comes with tons of pre-designed form templates to allow you to create forms you need in an instant. </p>\n<p>To collect and display user reviews on your website, you can use its blog post submission template with some customization. For more details, see this guide on how to <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/how-to-allow-users-to-leave-a-review-on-your-wordpress-site/\" target=\"_blank\">display user reviews on your WordPress site</a>. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get started with WPForms today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">3. OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software.jpg\" alt=\"OptinMonster Best Conversion Optimization Software\" width=\"560\" height=\"260\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-155241\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/optinmonster-conversion-optimization-software-300x139.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">OptinMonster</a> is the most powerful lead generation software in the market and the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-popup-plugins/\">best WordPress popup plugin</a>. It allows you to create stunning popup forms on your website and turn more visitors into subscribers. </p>\n<p>Using OptinMonster, you can create highly customized popups with social proof content. </p>\n<p>For example, you can see the screenshot below. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/socialproofpopupwordpres.png\" alt=\"Social Proof Popup with OptinMonster\" width=\"620\" height=\"408\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210784\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/socialproofpopupwordpres.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/socialproofpopupwordpres-300x197.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>In the image, you can see how our founder <a href=\"https://syedbalkhi.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Syed Balkhi</a>, has added social proof content.</p>\n<p>Also, you can use OptinMonster as a FOMO plugin. It allows you to <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-add-a-countdown-timer-in-wordpress/\">create countdown timer</a> to boost your eCommerce sales.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Get started with OptinMonster today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/ovation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Thrive Ovation</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/ovation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/thriveovationtestimonialwpplugin.png\" alt=\"Thrive Ovation WordPress Testimonial Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"242\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210786\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/thriveovationtestimonialwpplugin.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/thriveovationtestimonialwpplugin-300x117.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Similar to the user reviews, testimonials are highly effective social proof content you can use on your website. </p>\n<p>Testimonials are usually words of admiration and recommendation from the happy customers of a business. Adding testimonials to your website helps to increase trust and boost your site conversions. </p>\n<p>Adding testimonials in WordPress is easy with the simple <a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/ovation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Thrive Ovation</a> plugin. It offers you simple ways to gather and display testimonials on your website. </p>\n<p>Thrive Ovation enables you to transform any WordPress comment, social media comment on Facebook and Twitter into a beautiful testimonial with ease. It also lets you create testimonial landing pages to collect testimonials. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://thrivethemes.com/ovation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Thrive Ovation today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/shared-counts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Shared Counts</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/shared-counts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/shared-counts-wordpress-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"Shared Counts Best WordPress Social Media Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"198\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-162128\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/shared-counts-wordpress-plugin.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/shared-counts-wordpress-plugin-300x96.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Displaying social share counts is one of the most popular social proof marketing techniques in use today. </p>\n<p>Most websites display social share buttons and share counts on their blog posts. Doing so helps to prove your credibility, and also urges the new users to share your content.  </p>\n<p>You can easily add share buttons and show the shared counts for your WordPress articles using the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/shared-counts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shared Counts</a> plugin. It is fast and easy to use social media plugin for WordPress. </p>\n<p>Using this plugin, you can insert social share buttons before and/or after post content, and also show the total shares. It includes the popular social platforms Facebook, Pinterest, Yummly, and Twitter, and more. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/shared-counts/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Shared Counts today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Constant Contact</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/constantcontact.png\" alt=\"Constant Contact Email Marketing Tool\" width=\"620\" height=\"300\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-201594\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/constantcontact.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/constantcontact-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Another simple social proofing technique is to display your email subscribers’ count. Websites usually add ‘Join XX number of our subscribers’ message in their email sign-up forms and show that on their sidebars. </p>\n<p>You can see similar email subscription form on our blog, i.e., MonsterInsights Blog’s sidebar too.</p>\n<p>You can create similar type of sign-up form on your site by integrating with an <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-email-newsletter-tools-compared-pros-and-cons/\">email marketing service</a>. While there’re many options in the market, we recommend you to use <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Constant Contact</a>. </p>\n<p>It is the best email marketing software which lets you create an <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/why-collect-emails-benefits-of-building-an-email-list/\">email list</a> easily and send highly effective emails to your subscribers. </p>\n<p>The best way to create a signup form in WordPress with Constant Contact integration is by using WPForms plugin. </p>\n<p>It lets you connect your sign up form with your Constant Contact account and show the number of subscribers in WordPress. For more details, see this guide on <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/docs/how-to-connect-constant-contact-with-wpforms/\" target=\"_blank\">connecting Constant Contact with WPForms</a>. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/constant-contact/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Constant Contact today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/beeketing-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Beeketing for WooCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/beeketing-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/beeketingforwoocommerce.png\" alt=\"Beeketing for WooCommerce Social Proof Plugin\" width=\"620\" height=\"225\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210787\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/beeketingforwoocommerce.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/beeketingforwoocommerce-300x109.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you have a <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-create-a-woocommerce-store/\">WooCommerce store</a>, then you can show many types of social proof statistics to your store visitors. </p>\n<p>For example, you can display how many people viewed and bought products. Similarly, you can show who recently purchased your product. </p>\n<p>If you want these features, then <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/beeketing-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Beeketing for WooCommerce</a> is the perfect plugin for you. It is a free <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-woocommerce-plugins-and-extensions/\">WordPress WooCommerce plugin</a> with plenty of amazing features. </p>\n<p>Not just social proof, it also includes many FOMO plugin features. You can add a sale countdown clock, low-stock indicator, limited time discounts, etc. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/beeketing-for-woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Beeketing for WooCommerce today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to find the best social proof WordPress plugins to boost your sales. You may also want to see our handpicked list of <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-wordpress-plugins-and-tools-for-marketers/\">best WordPress plugins</a> to grow your website faster. </p>\n<p>And don’t forget to follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more WordPress tips.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-social-proof-wordpress-plugins-to-boost-your-sales/\">7 Best WordPress Plugins &#038; Tools to Add Social Proof and Boost Your Sales [2019]</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/best-social-proof-wordpress-plugins-to-boost-your-sales/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"Announcing MonsterInsights 7.7 – LifterLMS Integration, Expanded Page Insights, and More\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:181:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/announcing-monsterinsights-7-7-lifterlms-integration/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=announcing-monsterinsights-7-7-lifterlms-integration\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/announcing-monsterinsights-7-7-lifterlms-integration/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 20 Jun 2019 14:12:37 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"page insights\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"lifterlms\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"LMS plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"site health check\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/?p=210750\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:695:\"<p>For the past few weeks, our developers have been working hard on improving MonsterInsights and adding a new integration. Today we’re excited to announce the release of MonsterInsights 7.7, which comes with easy LifterLMS tracking and improvements to our admin bar page insights. Plus, it also integrates with the new WordPress Site Health Check feature! [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/announcing-monsterinsights-7-7-lifterlms-integration/\">Announcing MonsterInsights 7.7 &#8211; LifterLMS Integration, Expanded Page Insights, and More</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Keri Engel\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5135:\"<p>For the past few weeks, our developers have been working hard on improving MonsterInsights and adding a new integration.</p>\n<p>Today we’re excited to announce the release of MonsterInsights 7.7, which comes with easy <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/lifterlms/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">LifterLMS</a> tracking and improvements to our admin bar page insights. Plus, it also integrates with the new WordPress Site Health Check feature!</p>\n<p>Here are all the details&#8230;</p>\n<h3>One-Click LifterLMS eCommerce Analytics</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/refer/lifterlms/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">LifterLMS</a> is a learning management system plugin that lets you easily create and sell courses online. </p>\n<p>Selling courses is a great way to <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/make-money-online/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">make money online</a>. Truly understanding your audience is crucial for the success of your online courses. But keeping track of all the data on your subscriptions and downloads can be a hassle in Google Analytics.</p>\n<p>That’s why we’ve added one-click setup of LifterLMS tracking to MonsterInsights.</p>\n<p>Now with the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/addon/ecommerce/\">MonsterInsights eCommerce addon</a>, it’s easier than ever to track all your online course sales and downloads!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/monsterinsights-lifterlms-ecommerce-tracking.png\" alt=\"LifterLMS ecommerce analytics tracking\" width=\"620\" height=\"541\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210753\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/monsterinsights-lifterlms-ecommerce-tracking.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/monsterinsights-lifterlms-ecommerce-tracking-300x262.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<h3>Extended Page Insights &#8211; See Any Page&#8217;s Stats at a Glance</h3>\n<p>With Page Insights addon, you can quickly see stats for your WordPress posts or pages. The Page Insights addon allows you to quickly view important metrics like: new visitors, page views, bounce rate, time on page, page load time, and exits.</p>\n<p>Now, we’ve extended this feature so that it works for ALL content on your site &#8211; not just single posts and pages.</p>\n<p>That’s right, now you can instantly see the stats of any content, including custom post types, product category pages, and <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/addons/form-pages-addon/\" title=\"Form Landing Pages for WPForms\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">form landing pages</a>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/monsterinsights-page-insights-reports.jpg\" alt=\"wordpress page insights analytics\" width=\"620\" height=\"370\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-168228\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/monsterinsights-page-insights-reports.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/monsterinsights-page-insights-reports-300x179.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<h3>WordPress Site Health Checks Integration</h3>\n<p>Did you know that WordPress 5.2 included a new feature called Site Health? It monitors your site automatically and helps you to debug common issues.</p>\n<p>MonsterInsights now integrates with Site Health Check in WordPress, so you can double check your setup at a glance:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/monsterinsights-site-health-check.png\" alt=\"MonsterInsights WordPress site health check\" width=\"560\" height=\"495\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-210754\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/monsterinsights-site-health-check.png 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/monsterinsights-site-health-check-300x265.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></p>\n<p>All these new features are available now, so <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/pricing/\">click here to get started with MonsterInsights Pro today</a>!</p>\n<p>That’s all for this update! The whole team here thanks you for all your support in making MonsterInsights the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" title=\"Best Google Analytics Plugin for WordPress\">best Google analytics WordPress plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>Want to be the first to know about the next release? Be sure to subscribe to our email newsletter and follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/monsterinsights\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a>.</p>\n<p><em>Keri and the MonsterInsights Team</em></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/announcing-monsterinsights-7-7-lifterlms-integration/\">Announcing MonsterInsights 7.7 &#8211; LifterLMS Integration, Expanded Page Insights, and More</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/announcing-monsterinsights-7-7-lifterlms-integration/fee